So here we have the left-hand side exactly equal to the right hand side.

Or suppose <math>\textbf{x} = \monzo{0 & -3 & -5}</math> and <math>\textbf{y} = \monzo{6 & 6 & 6}</math>, and <math>q = 2</math>:


